# App Router Layering Rules

- `src/app/**/page.tsx` should be **routing only**:
  - Read `params`, render a shell, no business logic.
  - Avoid direct HCM calls and heavy state management in pages.

- Prefer this shape:

```tsx
// ✅ Good
export default async function Page({ params }: { params: Promise<{ id: string }> }) {
  const { id } = await params;
  return <SomeShell id={id} />;
}
```

- Place orchestration in feature shells/components under `src/features/**`.

